value.0: A big black cat with a white nose.
This simple oil painting shows a very old mage shaking hands with an even older mage. Both are smiling broadly and behind them a simmering cauldron can be seen.
A shopping list and notes on planar traveling. Beneath the explanation on how to open a gate to another dimension the words "P.S. - dont forgett to feed mister snuffles." stand written.
These exotic jars are filled with various foreign spices and teas.
